OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBoohoo could shut factory  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fafter BBC investigation    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Boohoo is considering closing its      
OL,6, first-ever manufacturing site after a  
OL,7, BBC investigation found it had broken  
OL,8, promises to make clothes ethically.    
OL,10,FThe site in Thurmaston Lane, Leicester,
OL,11,Fopened in 2022, with plans for it to   
OL,12,Falso be used as a training facility.   
OL,14,FBut a reporter at the firm's           
OL,15,Fheadquarters saw evidence of staff     
OL,16,Fpressuring suppliers to drive prices   
OL,17,Fdown, even after deals had been agreed.
OL,19,FBoohoo said the plans were not related 
OL,20,Fto the BBC Panorama investigation.     
